        "negate": "Sine.out → in; out → Add.b turns a sum into a subtraction — flips any field's sign. (Output.z floors at 0, so don't feed it directly.)",
        "one-minus": "Depth.depth → in; out → Palette.t flips the colormap so FAR pins take the hot end — the quick invert for any 0-1 field.",
