        "power": "Depth.depth → in, EXPONENT 2; out → Palette.t squeezes the hot colours onto only the nearest pins.",
        "quantize": "Depth.depth → in, STEPS 6; out → Output.z terraces the cloud into flat depth shelves.",
        "radial-ripple": "Raise AMP, then Ripple.height → Output.z: rings pulse from CENTERX/CENTERY. Expose those and wire Hand Position.x/y — the ripple follows your hand.",
        "receive": "Set CHANNEL to match a Send: out carries that Send's field with no wire across the canvas. Empty or looping channels read 0.",
